data.description: This lovely 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom Colonial home is located on a private cul-de-sac street.  The living room features premium flooring and a large window allowing in natural light. This flooring extends into the spacious eat-in kitchen and first-floor half bath. Sliding glass doors in the kitchen lead to a screened in sunroom overlooking the fully fenced backyard.  Three sizable bedrooms and one full bathroom can be found on the second floor.
